@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@
+# Pruned
+
+- Format registry / strategy / `Exporter` base class keyed on format
+  (json/csv/markdown). Rejected: only ONE real variant (JSON) is required
+  now. The acceptance asks for JSON only; csv/markdown are speculative.
+  Abstracting before the 2nd real variant exists is premature. Add the
+  seam when the second format actually lands.
+- Touching store.py (e.g. an `export`/serialize helper). Rejected: not
+  needed — `store.load` already returns the array; writing JSON is one
+  json.dump in the cli handler.
