@@ -0,0 +1,11 @@
+# Corridor: E1-B-2-export
+
+Add an `export <outfile>` subcommand that writes all notes as a JSON array.
+
+Seam: `cli.build_parser` (subparser registration) + a new `cmd_export`
+handler that reads notes via `store.load(args.store)`. No store change —
+`load` already returns the note list.
+
+## Paths
+
+- cli_notes/cli.py
